Package scriptmanager.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayUtilities
    Generally useful array manipulations.
    BAMUtilities  
    BEDUtilities
    Class containing a set of shared methods to be used across script classes.
    CDTUtilities
    This class was created to parse and validate CDT files and counting the number of columns and is based on originally tool-specific methods.
    ColorSeries
    Fixed preset color palettes for figure generation.
    DNAShapeReference
    This class stores reference collections on DNA shape as constants for tools in the scripts package.
    ExtensionFileFilter
    Filters files such as BAI, BAM, BED, CDT, FASTA, FA, GFF, TAB for the FileSelection tool based on the extension of the filename.
    FASTAUtilities
    Utilities for sequence manipulation.
    FileSelection
    Various kinds of file selectors used by the window_interface objects to restrict user input selection options.
    GenomeSizeReference
    Create a genomic chromosome/contig size reference that is essentially defined as an ArrayList chromsome/contig names and a parallel ArrayList storing each chromsome/contig's length (in bp).
    GZipUtilities
    This class contains static methods for parsing files and input streams to determine GZip-format information.
    SimilarityMetric
